libunity README
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

LibUnity is library for instrumenting- and integrating with all aspects of the
Unity shell (lp:unity). This is not a library used in the implementation
of the Unity shell itself (lp:unity does not link against it), but a library to
be consumed by clients that wants to do deep integration with the Unity shell.

The development focus of libunity can always be found on lp:libunity. The stable
series of libunity are listed below:

 * lp:libunity/3.0 - API+ABI stable. Shipped with Ubuntu 11.04 "Natty Narwhal"
